entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have completed several tasks for Reelo Baruk, and proved yourself enough that he's sent you to Ree-Yees for more work in the palace.
entries.journal_entry_description: There are plenty of people who live or work in Jabba's Palace who need things done. You're the person to do those things.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Jabba has a lot of people who pay him for protection. Unfortunately for the Alkharan bandits, they've been raiding some of these people. Jabba wants you to teach them a lesson. Kill 10 Alkharan bandits. You have been given a waypoint to an area where they have been seen recently.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: Good work. Jabba wants you to take care of some of Valarian's soldiers who are skulking around the Palace.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: "Good work. Jabba wants you to take care of some of Valarian's soldiers who are skulking around the Palace."
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Lady Valarian's underlings have been skulking around the palace, and Jabba wants to scare them away. Kill 11 of Valarian's soldiers.
entries.task03_comm_message_text: Some of Valarian's people are buying up gambling debts. Take the vouchers from them so we can cash in ourselves.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: "Some of Valarian's people are buying up gambling debts. Take the vouchers from them so we can cash in ourselves."
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Reelo wants you to attack some of Lady Valarian's bookies and collect the gambling vouchers they've been buying and carrying around. Bring back 7 of them.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Return to Reelo Baruk in Jabba's Palace.
